# E-commerce Web Application (MVP)

## Background

The company plans to launch an online shopping platform to allow customers to browse products and place orders online.

Phase 1 focuses on delivering core purchasing functionality.

---

## Objectives

- Enable user registration and login
- Allow browsing and searching products
- Support add-to-cart functionality
- Enable checkout and order placement

---

## Scope

### In Scope
- User authentication
- Product listing
- Shopping cart
- Checkout process
- Order confirmation

### Out of Scope
- Payment gateway integration (mock payment only)
- Admin management portal
- Recommendation engine

---

## Stakeholders

- Product Owner
- Business Analyst
- Development Team
- QA Team
- End Users
